        <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
            <head>Scope and Content </head>
            <p>Governor Henry grants Carson 300 acres of land in Campbell County, Va. Carson was the
                assignee of Richard Stith, assignee of John Hall, assignee of Aaron Quarles. Issued
                by virtue of Land Office Treasury Warrant #15,160 dated 1783 February 25. Signed by
                John Harvie, Re{gister} L{and} O{ffice}. Printed form with manuscript insertions.
                Bears seal of Virginia. </p>
        </scopecontent>
